quran[7{c,v,t}:
39,68,aur jab sor phonka jaye ga to jo log aasman mein hain aur jo zameen mein hain sab be hosh ho kar gir parrin ge magar woh jis ko khuda chahay. phir doosri dafaa phonka jaye ga to foran sab kharray ho kar dekhnay lagen ge
39,69,aur zameen apne perwar-digaar ke noor se jagmaga uthay gi aur ( aamaal ki ) kitaab ( khol kar ) rakh di jaye gi aur paighambar aur ( aur ) gawah haazir kiye jayen ge aur un mein insaaf ke sath faislakiya jaye ga aur be insafi nahi ki jaye gi
39,70,aur jis shakhs ne jo amalkiya hoga is ko is ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur jo kuch yeh karte hain is ko sab ki khabar hai
39,71,aur kafiroon ko giroh giroh bana kar jahannum ki taraf le jayen ge. yahan taq ke jab woh is ke paas poanch jayen ge to is ke darwazay khol diye jayen ge to is ke Darogha un se kahin ge kekiya tumahray paas tum hi mein se paighambar nahi aeye they jo tum ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki ayatain parh parh kar sunaate aur is din ke paish anay se darate they kahin ge kyun nahi lekin kafiroon ke haq mein azaab ka hukum mutahaqqiq hochuka tha
39,72,kaha jaye ga ke dozakh ke darwazon mein daakhil hojao hamesha is mein raho ge. taqqabur karne walon ka bura thikana hai
39,73,aur jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ko giroh giroh bana kar bahisht ki taraf le jayen ge yahan taq ke jab is ke paas poanch jayen ge aur is ke darwazay khol diye jayen ge to is ke Darogha un se kahin ke tum par salam tum bohat achay rahay. ab is mein hamesha ke liye daakhil hojao
39,74,woh kahin ge ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne apne wada ko hum se sacha kardiya aur hum ko is zameen ka waris bana diya hum bahisht mein jis makaan mein chahain rahen to ( achay ) amal karne walon ka badla bhi kaisa khoob hai
